        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Some things that I take as fact.</P><P>Solo:<BR>Pet does 50% damage pet gets 50% xp<BR>Pet does less than 50% damage you get 100% of the xp</P><P>Group<BR>Pet does 50% damage (i.e. outdamage the entire group including other peoples pets) pet takes 50% of the xp.<BR>Pet does not outdamage the group pet takes no xp.</P><P>These are based off of information gained from ShowEQ. </P><P>The workings of ShowEQ.</P><P>One of the things that ShowEQ can do for you is show you the amount of xp that you get for any particular kill. Using this method you can determin who gets what xp by doing a few control kills and then letting your pet kill something solo.</P><P>Philiak Mortus Lv.49 Necromancer of Xev<BR>Slisik n00bie Shaman of Povar<BR>Sam: Where should I put this thing so that it doesnt hurt anyone we know or care about?<BR>Max: Out the window Sam. There's nobody but strangers out there.<BR><a href="http://www.pvponline.com" target="_blank">www.pvponline.com</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
